Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.58,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The 737 MAX was sold as a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:06.13,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,familiar airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.18,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,That was the commercial\Npromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.46,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Airlines could keep crews,\Nschedules, and training
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.83,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,close to the old 737.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.94,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Then Boeing put larger CFM\NLeap engines
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.31,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,on the aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.12,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,They sat farther forward\Nand higher on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.98,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the wing, and under\Ncertain high angle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,of attack conditions, the\Njet could pitch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.70,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,up differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.41,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,MCAS was built to make\Nthat new
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.62,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,behavior feel familiar,\Nbut the system could
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.83,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,move the stabilizer from\None angle of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.04,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,attack sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.46,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Pilots were not clearly\Ntrained that it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,existed by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.40,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,After Lionair 610, the\Nwarning still was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,not reclassified fast\Nenough as an architectural
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.71,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:50.63,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The plane had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:52.81,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The story told to the\Npeople flying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.03,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,it had not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:58.00,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
